3 SENATE BILL NO. 1927 By: Standridge
4
5
6 An Act relating to felony offenses; amending Section
15, Chapter 366, O.S.L. 2024 (21 O.S. Supp. 2025,
7 Section 20O), which relates to Class D2 offenses;
adding offense; updating statutory references;
8 updating statutory language; creating certain felony
offense; providing penalty; defining term; providing
9 for codification; and providing an effective date.
10
11
12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY Section 15, Chapter 366, O.S.L.
14 2024 (21 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 20O), is amended to read as
15 follows:
16 Section 20O. A. Upon the effective date of this act On or
17 after January 1, 2026, Class D2 shall include the following criminal
18 offenses:
19 1. Attempt Attempting to escape from a penitentiary, as
20 provided for in Section 434 of Title 21 of the Oklahoma Statutes
21 this title;
22 2. Attempt Attempting to escape from prison, not a
23 penitentiary, as provided for in Section 436 of Title 21 of the
24 Oklahoma Statutes this title;
